OL,3,CNew mental health strategy revealed as
OL,4,Ccrisis referrals rise by a third
OL,6,FJersey's Health and Social Services
OL,7,FDepartment have published a new
OL,8,Fstrategy for mental health provision
OL,9,Fthat focuses on the importance of
OL,10,Fprevention and early intervention.
OL,12,FIt comes after crisis referrals to
OL,13,FAdult Mental Health Services rose by
OL,14,F38% in 2025.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
