OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1774353808
OL,3,CNew mental health strategy revealed as
OL,4,Ccrisis referrals rise by a third
OL,6,FInformed by a 10-month-long
OL,7,Finvestigation into existing mental
OL,8,Fhealth provision for both adults and
OL,9,Fchildren, the strategy outlines a need
OL,10,Fto strengthen services that prevent
OL,11,Fpeople from reaching crisis point -
OL,12,Falongside improving access to support,
OL,13,Fand coordinating different resources
OL,14,Fmore effectively.
OL,16,FDiscussions with existing patients and
OL,17,Fprofessionals working in mental health
OL,18,Fsettings also highlighted some of
OL,19,Ftheir current concerns and
OL,20,Fdifficulties.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1774353808
OL,3,CNew mental health strategy revealed as
OL,4,Ccrisis referrals rise by a third
OL,6,FSome of these comments included:
OL,8,FThis research has led to four broad
OL,9,Fareas which need to be improved. These
OL,10,Fare:
OL,12,FEnsuring people have the tools they
OL,13,Fneed to tackle mental health
OL,14,Fdifficulties before they reach a
OL,15,Fcrisis point.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1774353808
OL,3,CNew mental health strategy revealed as
OL,4,Ccrisis referrals rise by a third
OL,6,FEnsuring everyone knows what services
OL,7,Fare available and how to access them,
OL,8,Fand developing ways for these services
OL,9,Fto work in a more "joined-up way", so
OL,10,Fthat people do not feel "passed
OL,11,Fbetween services".
OL,13,FEnsuring people know where to go in a
OL,14,Fmental health crisis, and reducing
OL,15,Freliance on the Accident and Emergency
OL,16,FDepartment to tackle these crises. The
OL,17,Fstrategy hopes to develop crisis
OL,18,Fservices that are "joined-up, trauma-
OL,19,Finformed, and available 24 hours a day
OL,20,Ffor all ages".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1774353808
OL,3,CNew mental health strategy revealed as
OL,4,Ccrisis referrals rise by a third
OL,6,FDelivering services that are focused
OL,7,Fon recovery that is defined by "long-
OL,8,Fterm wellbeing, confidence, and
OL,9,Fquality of life", even when living
OL,10,Fwith ongoing mental health
OL,11,Fdifficulties.
OL,13,FIn a statement, Jersey's Children and
OL,14,FFamilies Minister, Constable Richard
OL,15,FVibert, said the strategy is "designed
OL,16,Fto make sure support is there for
OL,17,Fpeople of all ages, from early
OL,18,Fchildhood right through to later life".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1774353808
OL,3,CNew mental health strategy revealed as
OL,4,Ccrisis referrals rise by a third
OL,6,FHe explained: "Over the next five
OL,7,Fyears, we want to build a community
OL,8,Fwhere mental health is understood,
OL,9,Fwhere help is easier to find for
OL,10,Ffamilies and individuals, and where no
OL,11,Fone feels they have to cope alone."
OL,13,FThe Health and Social Services
OL,14,FMinister, Deputy Tom Binet, added:
OL,15,F"Supporting islanders' mental health
OL,16,Fis a fundamental priority for this
OL,17,FGovernment.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
